    <item>
      <title>通胀意外支持菲律宾央行宽松计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/philippine-central-bank-head-favors-baby-steps-in-easing-cycle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾央行行长伊莱雷莫洛纳 (Eli Remolona) 表示，由于通胀的惊人放缓支持其进一步放松政策，菲律宾可能将采取每季度一次的降息措施，将基准利率在 2025 年之前下调约 175 个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/philippine-central-bank-head-favors-baby-steps-in-easing-cycle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 09:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
